Add `cursor_style` and `cursor_blink` options to opencode TUI config.

Upstream's TUI package ships only color/scroll/diff settings for cursor
appearance. This patch:

  1. Adds a `CursorStyle` schema literal (`"block" | "line" | "underline"`)
     and registers `cursor_style` + `cursor_blink` on the TUI config schema.
  2. Threads the resolved cursor style into every `TextareaRenderable` JSX
     site so all text inputs honor the configured style and blink setting.

